      • openCamera

        public static boolean openCamera(@NonNull
                                 CameraController.Select select,
                                 @Nullable
                                 java.lang.Runnable runnable,
                                 @Nullable
                                 android.os.Handler handler)
        Open camera for capture. Camera opens asynchronously, therefore to wait for the camera to open before continuing execution, pass in a runnable and its thread to run on.
        Parameters:
        select - Which camera (FRONT, BACK, or EXTERNAL)
        runnable - (Optional) Execution continues with this Runnable
        handler - (Optional) Runnable is executed on this thread (camera controller thread default)
        Returns:
        True if camera is opening, false if request is unsuccessful
